description:
&lt;p&gt;MAIN DUTIES&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Helpdesk Operator shall:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Comply with EFM Helpdesk Standard Operating Procedures(SOPs)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Log calls/work orders directly on to the Helpdesk Database using CAFM software. Work orders requests may be received by telephone, email or in person.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Schedule jobs to tradespersons through the CAFM system to ensure work allocated fits within shift patterns and is within SLA periods.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Allocate work request to the maintenance team as specified, this includes use of 2 way radio to communicate priority 1 and 2 tasks and use of CAFM planner in accordance with agreed scheduling procedures.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Issue planned preventative maintenance (PPMs) work orders to the maintenance team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Track job progress against predetermined KPIs including maximum allowable response and rectification times and implementing escalation procedures.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Report back to clients and requesters on job progress and on completion via automated email reply. Updating assets history with works record sheets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Produce basic or scheduled reports on CAFM data as requested. Use the data from CAFM to produce Excel reports&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Maintenance of archiving Work Order requests, completed Work Order Job Sheets and PPMs in accordance with procedures.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;These duties detailed are intended to give the post holder an appreciation of the role envisaged for the Helpdesk Operator and the range of duties to be undertaken.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Any other duties required to ensure an effective and efficient helpdesk service is delivered in accordance with the CAFM system and operating procedures.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will also be expected to carry out general administrative duties to within the EFM business unit to provide a seamless service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameCheryl HarrellTelephone number01702-435555 Ext 7724&lt;/p&gt;
